This is a 32 spawns Map for the counter strike gun game mod, but you can also play it as a team deathmatch map.
it a non-symetrycal map wich is rare for the gungame , but it works perfectly.
there are 2 playable levels , 1 indoor with an undeground hangar, 1 outdoor with several bunkers.

Enjoy it ;)
